    "result": {"data":{"cur":{"id":"1e6eedb4-a571-573a-84f7-63ff7a3bb8c8","html":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://nomadcoders.co/kokoa-clone/lobby\">노마드코더 - 코코아톡 클론코딩</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"노트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%85%B8%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"노트 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>노트</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1-강의-627--640\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EA%B0%95%EC%9D%98-627--640\" aria-label=\"1 강의 627  640 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 강의 #6.27 ~ #6.40</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>tip. <code class=\"language-text\">position</code>이 <code class=\"language-text\">fixed</code>인 경우 layer가 다르기 때문에 navbar 같은거 만들때 fixed로 인해 그 이후 요소랑 겹침 현상 일어 날 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>해결 방안</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>body쪽에 <code class=\"language-text\">padding-top</code> 주는게 제일 무난한 방법이라 생각.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"animation---forwards\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#animation---forwards\" aria-label=\"animation   forwards permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>animation - forwards</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>애니메이션에 forwards 속성을 넣으면 애니메이션이 끝나도 변한 값 유지</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">visibility:hidden</code>은 임시방편, 정석은 자바스크립트로 처리해야 한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>예시</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@keyframes</span> hideSplashScreen</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token selector\">from</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token selector\">to</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token property\">opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token property\">visibility</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> hidden<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token selector\">.splash-screen</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n...\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 동작 후에 opicity가 1로 돌아온다. */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token property\">animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> hideSplashScreen 0.5s ease-in-out<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 동작 후에 opicity가 0으로 유지되고 visibility hidden */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token property\">animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> hideSplashScreen 0.5s ease-in-out forwards<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"will-change\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#will-change\" aria-label=\"will change permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>will-change</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>브라우저에게 어떤 속성이 변할지 알려줄 때 사용</li>\n<li>알려줌으로 그래픽카드를 이용해 애니메이션을 가속화 한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"state-selector--focus-within\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#state-selector--focus-within\" aria-label=\"state selector  focus within permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>state selector > focus-within</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>선택요소의 element가 focus되어 있다면 이라는 뜻</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>예시</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\